{"tid":129079,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"開左個關於科研既fb page同香港人科普下","createTime":"2017-02-21T10:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T04:01:40.000Z","uid":86628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f7c2c2eebf765efc24cf9dacc2b8691b9756d9","tid":129079,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 眼見其實有唔知香港人年青一輩有唔少人其實係投身於科研<br />\n但係又無乜人在特別有個香港既科研交流平台,講下D辛酸之類<br />\n同時又唔似有人會特別為香港人製作一D特別有名既最新生物科技既講解,一般都好流於表面<br />\n唔想大家只係停留於中學大學D考試層面,而係更貼近最新published journal paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想開呢個PAGE乜都想講,想製片想發嗡風,想分享自己research既一d有趣片段,又想同大家交流下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望巴打入黎比個like同埋留下言，<br />\n黎緊會開埋個YOUTUBE CHANNEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好快有片出 希望多多支持,入黎比個LIKE丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝大家支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ScientificNerd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FScientificNerd%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=258e05cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ScientificNerd/</a>"},{"pid":"86147e1700d24dac180c81b0e1f8cb91e1e8f20f","tid":129079,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8bd88b38b8fa71e7b3aec47bcf150fea9b37b7","tid":129079,"uid":86628,"like":0,"di